Author: Wegathetix Created:2023-01-03

Summary
CEX like trading experience by eliminating wallet confirmations.

Abstract
A trader will be able to interact with the Kwenta protocol (for example: place a market/limit buy order) without wallet confirmations.

Motivation
Confirmation-less execution will improve user experience, especially for frequent traders.

Specification
Trader preloads gas fees and starts trading. 
